@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<h1>Fabric / Power BI embed sample</h1>

<p>
    This app demonstrates <strong>server-side</strong> embed token generation (service principal) and
    Blazor lifecycle patterns for switching between a semantic-model report and a paginated report.
</p>

<ol class="steps">
    <li>
        Copy values into configuration or <code>dotnet user-secrets</code> (see comments in
        <code>appsettings.Development.json</code>). Never commit the client secret.
    </li>
    <li>
        In Power BI / Fabric admin: allow service principals; add your app to the workspace.
    </li>
    <li>
        Open <a href="/semantic">Semantic report</a> and <a href="/paginated">Paginated report</a>.
        If the paginated report uses semantic models, set <code>PowerBi:PaginatedDatasetIds</code>.
    </li>
</ol>
